{"tid":2272472,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國總統有不爭取連任的嗎？","createTime":"2020-11-05T05:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T05:59:00.000Z","uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d02d2db5458f34b1df8f6513742d2ee885cbb09","tid":2272472,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-48661357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-48661357&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4Cvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=6b0d5eb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-48661357&h=a51a3a29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-48661357</a><br />\n1.<br />\n事實上，美國總統不爭取連任是非常罕見的。回顧歷史，只有五位總統「主動退休」。他們分別是：<br />\n    詹姆斯&middot;波爾克（James K Polk）：1845-1849<br />\n    拉瑟福德&middot;海斯（Rutherford B Hayes）：1877 to 1881<br />\n    詹姆斯&middot;布坎南（James Buchanan）：1857 to 1861<br />\n    林登&middot;貝恩斯&middot;約翰遜（Lyndon Johnson）：1963 to 1969<br />\n    加爾文&middot;柯立芝（Calvin Coolidge）:1923 to 1929<br />\n約翰遜和柯立芝任期略長，是因為前任在位期間離世，他們首先完成遺留任期。<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n拜登今年78歲，若當選會成為最年老總統。如果下届爭取連任，將會再破記錄。<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\nLyndon Johnson和Calvin Coolidge所謂的不爭取連任，是因爲他們本來是副總統。他們就任就因爲Warren Harding和JFK於在任期間身亡。<br />\n<br />\n4.<br />\n如果拜登當選，而未來四年内因任何理由無法履行職務，賀錦麗便會補上，並很大機會爭取連任。<br />\n如果拜登."},{"pid":"e8038115301b985a24e4b2c93aa6ef7de29ee72d","tid":2272472,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"賀錦麗，第一個女黑人，女印度人總統 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c606bc90cce02bbbae6f31616877e9890d25a8","tid":2272472,"uid":259246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"漏撚咗個Truman <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354b8a2f3339a14f5adb29fd8337e6825ec077fd","tid":2272472,"uid":228995,"like